)2] 19: end for 20: t′ ← Sample an index from 1, 2, ..., R 21: for i = t′ to t′ + n do 22: si, ai, ri, γi, si+1 ← Retrieve a transition from M [i] 23: dθ ← dθ +∇θ′ [∑k l=1 ( ri − rli )2 + ( γi − γli
)2] 24: end for 25: Perform asynchronous update of θ using dθ 26: if T mod Itarget == 0 then 27: Update the target network θ− ← θ 28: end if 29: end while
